data.description: Welcome to this exceptional 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom country-style home, a property that offers a multitude of opportunities to enjoy its expansive space. Whether you have a large family, a multi-generational household, plans to run a business from home, or simply love entertaining, this residence has it all.  As you explore this remarkable location, you'll discover a spacious warehouse that significantly enhances the versatility of your property. With ample room for RVs or campers, your options for storage or expansion are virtually limitless.  The sellers have thoughtfully updated a substantial portion of this home, ensuring that all improvements are properly permitted and in compliance with the highest standards. The kitchen has been thoughtfully redesigned, seamlessly integrating it with the dining room, creating a welcoming space where the entire family can gather and bond over meals and special moments.  The bathrooms have undergone extensive remodeling, complete with new plumbing installations, ensuring both style and functionality. One of the most transformative changes made to this property was the removal of the dropped-down ceiling, which has been replaced with a striking cathedral ceiling. This not only adds a sense of spaciousness but also brings an inviting airiness to the home.  For those with beloved canine companions, your fur-babies will relish the opportunity to roam and play in the securely fenced outdoor area designed specifically for their enjoyment and safety. This rare country-style home is a canvas for your vision, offering countless possibilities for comfortable family living, multi-generational arrangements, business endeavors, and entertainment. With meticulous updates and a versatile warehouse on the premises, you have the haven of your dreams.  Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable residence your own.
